achievements.title: A Quest for Strength Fulfilled
achievements.description: After countless battles and considerable struggle, you've arrived. Is this the end of your quest for strength? The answer...lies within.

achievements.title: Get Your Game Face On!
achievements.description: Where's your face, dingus? Get your butt to the avatar creator and sort yourself out! Crying shame we can't fix that attitude of yours while we're at it.

achievements.title: So This Is the Battle Hub...
achievements.description: Ah, yes. Welcome to the Battle Hub. I do not know what you seek, but please, enjoy yourself. That is the purpose for which it was built, after all.

achievements.title: First Encounters
achievements.description: Start by fighting a match in the Battle Hub. It doesn't matter if you win or lose. What matters is challenging yourself to take that first step.

achievements.title: There's Always Time for Training!
achievements.description: How's 30 matches in the Battle Hub sound? If yer not there yet, just keep at it! If ya wanna get sumo strong, ya can't be shy of the ring!

achievements.title: King of the Ring
achievements.description: Starting to get used to competition? Then set your sights on winning 30 Battle Hub matches. Gotta give yourself a challenge if you want to get anywhere in life.

achievements.title: Jungle-Sized Surprise
achievements.description: Ever hear of Extreme Battles? They're a little different from regular fights—a little more WILD. Try it out, and let your instincts take over!

achievements.title: Extreme Combat Training
achievements.description: If you can't adapt, you won't last five seconds on the battlefield. Fight 20 Extreme Battles. Perfect training to sharpen your judgement.

achievements.title: Over the Top Victory
achievements.description: 20 wins in Extreme Battle. Should be a snap for someone like you, yeah? Stomp this one flat, then aim for even greater heights! Bwahaha!

achievements.title: Becoming the Avatar
achievements.description: In Avatar Battles, you can battle others as an avatar―a self outside of your self. Go there, and experience all that such combat has to offer.

achievements.title: Fixin' for a Fight
achievements.description: Nothing gets my engine revving more than a brawl between avatars, live and in the flesh! Let's see you do 20 Avatar Battles!

achievements.title: The Struggle Over Self
achievements.description: An alternate form of combat, with an alternate path to victory. Get 20 wins in Avatar Battles. But don't obsess over the results. Let experience be your guide.

achievements.title: Gazing at the Peak
achievements.description: If you wanna match the one-and-only Jamie Siu, you'd better be early to the starting line. Give a Tournament a shot!

achievements.title: Steely Determination
achievements.description: The determination to stand in the ring and fight is what turns mind and muscle into tempered steel! Enter five Tournaments, and see for yourself!

achievements.title: Dominating Like a Ninja
achievements.description: Ninja can leap staircases in a single bound, but there's no skipping steps in training. Win ten Tournaments. It won't be easy, but you can do it.

achievements.title: Veteran of Battle
achievements.description: Kung fu is the result of ceaseless training. Do anything enough times, and you'll see results. So will you, once you fight in the Battle Hub 100 times.

achievements.title: Kickin' it Old School
achievements.description: Did you know you can play classic games at the Battle Hub Game Center? It's true! Cassette tapes and cartridges might be old...but they're still hecka rad.

achievements.title: Classic Leaderboard Champ
achievements.description: Ever try the Ranking Challenge at the Game Center? Give it a shot! It's important to always challenge yourself, even when it comes to games.

achievements.title: Entranced by Battle
achievements.description: Having an audience changes everything...and turns a mere fight into thrilling spectacle. Spectate a Battle Hub Match, and bear witness to glory.

achievements.title: Combat Analysis
achievements.description: In combat, you must constantly analyze the situation. Spectate an Extreme Battle, and hone your ability to read and react to the unexpected.

achievements.title: Watching Gets Me PUMPED!
achievements.description: Ah, there's nothing quite like a fight, one-on-one, in the flesh! If you wanna appreciate it too, go spectate an Avatar Battle!

achievements.title: Welcome to the Stable
achievements.description: Sounds like the Battle Hub has clubs you can join. Just like a sumo stable! You should join one! Ooh, I wonder if they have chanko stew...

achievements.title: Let the Praise Become Your Muscle
achievements.description: Hrrah! To fight before a cheering crowd is an honor shared by all wrestlers! Go on—try earning yourself a "Nice" fan of your own!

achievements.title: Gotta Be Popular! Uwo!
achievements.description: Uwo! My dream's to become famous, and make Mama proud! You should become famous too! Try gathering 200 "Nice" fans, for starters!

achievements.title: Spirits of Encouragement
achievements.description: Having outside support is a bit like having a spirit. You can't see them, but they lend you strength all the same. Get 600 "Nice" fans, and you'll feel strong too.

achievements.title: Pleased to Meet You!
achievements.description: I used to ask millions of questions as an agent. There's a lot you can learn from people just by talking to them—try chatting in the Battle Hub.

achievements.title: Coolheaded Analysis
achievements.description: Reviewing replay footage is a great way to learn from past fights. Watch with a calm, subjective eye, and you're bound to make some discoveries.

achievements.title: My Title, My Life
achievements.description: Earned any titles for your efforts yet? Me? Pfft. I don't need a title. I'm Jamie freakin' Siu!

achievements.title: Joining the Pack
achievements.description: A lone wolf is strong, but they're far more fearsome if they have a pack to call their own. So go on—try making some friends!

achievements.title: Fashion Leader
achievements.description: Clothing allows us to express ourselves. Know who else never changes their clothes? Animals. Change your outfit. Please.

achievements.title: Ready to Dance?
achievements.description: Have you had a chance to jam out at the DJ Booth in the Battle Hub, bud? Pick your favorite tunes, and light the dance floor aflame!

achievements.title: Up on the Big Screen
achievements.description: Sit down by the big monitor in the Battle Hub, and you can view all kinds of stuff. Man... Used to be me up there going wild on the big screen.

achievements.title: Neighborhood Peacekeeper
achievements.description: You gotta help people in need. I mean, that's the secret to keeping any city peaceful. So get out there and complete 22 sub-missions, got it?

achievements.title: Mastery's Bond
achievements.description: Once you find someone to call a master, you would do well to seek to deepen your bonds. Raise the bond with one of your masters to 100.

achievements.title: At Journey's End
achievements.description: Oh, you finished World Tour, did you? I suppose a word of congratulation is in order. I do hope your journey was a meaningful one.

achievements.title: Leaving the Nest
achievements.description: That's a wrap for basic training! You're a full-fledged fighting chickadee now, buddy. It's all up to you from here on out. Enjoy it!

achievements.title: Ha-dough-ken
achievements.description: I've worked a few odd jobs during my travels, and they all helped me with my training. You should take up a part-time job during your World Tour, as well.

achievements.title: Actions Speak Louder
achievements.description: Something in the way while you're walking through the city? Here's an easy solution: send it flyin' with a Master Action! Mm-mm-mmm... It's the little pleasures in life.

achievements.title: The Grand Jeté of 100 Battles
achievements.description: Fight 100 online battles via Fighting Ground. What's that? Too difficult, you say? If you wish to take on the world, there can be no other path.

achievements.title: Tales of the Valiant
achievements.description: Gonna need ya to head to the Fighting Ground and finish Arcade Mode once, buddy! It's time ya heard the stories of your fellow fighters!

achievements.title: Practical Training
achievements.description: You've heard of combo trials, I presume? It's time you practice attack sequences. I want you to finish 45 of them. It will be difficult, but I've the utmost faith in you.

achievements.title: Fighting Fledgling
achievements.description: You know how a swallow can fly at speeds of up to 200 kilometers an hour? Well, even they were chicks once. It's all about practice! Get yourself to Training Mode!

achievements.title: Fighters' Codex
achievements.description: Whoa, you seen these Character Guide things? Talk about rad! They've got all kinds of info about people's fighting styles and moves. Oh yeah, Bushinryu gets some rep too, naturally.

achievements.title: Taking Initiative
achievements.description: You want to learn street fighting fundamentals? Well, too bad, 'cause I'm not in the mood to take on any students. Go hit the Tutorials, kid.

achievements.title: Am I A Joke To You?
achievements.description: Go on a 20-0 scoring run in a single game

achievements.title: Keep Your Distance

achievements.title: Net Gain

achievements.title: Dirty Work
achievements.description: Get more rebounds, blocks, and assists than your opponent

achievements.title: Spreading The Love
achievements.description: Finish a game in which all 5 starters score double-digit points

achievements.title: Master of Hearts
achievements.description: Proof of a perfect completion of Tales of Hearts R. Thanks for playing! Your love and dedication are hugely appreciated!

achievements.title: Counteractivist
achievements.description: Bash, bang, pow! Your timing couldn't be more perfect! You don't fear enraged attacks—you welcome them with open arms!

achievements.title: Challenge Champ
achievements.description: No matter what it takes, you'll rise to the challenge! It's high time you were rewarded for your go-getting attitude!

achievements.title: 200-Hit Combo
achievements.description: Hit after hit after hit after hit after hit! You lay it on so thick and fast, the enemy doesn't stand a chance!

achievements.title: Spiria Superior
achievements.description: The strength of the bonds between us is the source of our greatest strength. Let the Spiria shine on!

achievements.title: Cross Chase Ace
achievements.description: A band of companions working in perfect harmony, and connected by unbreakable bonds—bonds that go beyond mere individuals and out into the fabric of the universe itself.

achievements.title: Chase Link Ace
achievements.description: Come on! Just one more second! And another! And another! Your unflappable perserverance has finally paid off!

achievements.title: Boo!
achievements.description: This award commemorates your uncanny ability to be taken unawares. You don't let the surprise grind your Spiria down, though—you thrive on it!

achievements.title: M2K
achievements.description: Day after day, from the dawn's early light to the setting of the sun, you slayed every single beast that crossed your path. Looking back, it's hard to tell now if your epic journey of slaughter took forever or the twinkling of an eye.

achievements.title: Max. Level Allstars
achievements.description: Awarded for training every character up to achieve their maximum potential. From here on out, it's just about learning how best to put that potential into practice!

achievements.title: Monster Collector
achievements.description: You have sought out creatures of all shapes and sizes and diligently recorded their every detail. It's high time your monstrous menagerie was appreciated in all its gory glory!

achievements.title: Item Hoarder
achievements.description: Your fine eye for a fine item has led to your being awarded this momentous accolade. You've experienced every effect the various objects of the world have to offer, and bathed in their beauty to your heart's content!

achievements.title: Marker Marker
achievements.description: You've tracked down every item marker out there, no matter how well-hidden. Is there nothing in this world you can't find?

achievements.title: Globetrotter
achievements.description: You've seen every inch of the whole wide world with your own two eyes, and this award proves it. It's a big old place out there, but as you now know, there's nothing to fear.

achievements.title: Maestrochef
achievements.description: You've spent more time in the kitchen than the Wonder Chef himself! He must be over the moon to have such a dedicated pupil as you! Maybe you'll be as buff as him one day, too!

achievements.title: Namcoin Classic Collection
achievements.description: You've collected every single Namcoin out there. Citrine is so happy she could die! Just don't go losing them before you hand them over to her, you hear?

achievements.title: Victory over the Grim Keeper
achievements.description: This hateful being likes nothing more than to watch his faithful scythe swing about the place causing mayhem. If Gall hadn't showed up just in the nick of time, he may have stopped Kor and co. at the very first hurdle.

achievements.title: Victory over Chalcedony
achievements.description: This nasty bundle of bowl-haircutted bad attitude has a Soma that lets him fly around in the air. He'd better give that piece of Kohaku's Spiria Core back, or he'll be sorry!

achievements.title: Victory over Amethyst
achievements.description: This supposedly world-famous hero would have you believe that you defeated him more through luck than anything else, but you know the real story.

achievements.title: Victory over the Sandworm
achievements.description: This self-satisfied slitherer was probably so full of beans as he wriggled his way beneath the sands because he'd swallowed a shard of unadulterated joy.

achievements.title: Victory over Chalcedony's Crew
achievements.description: A pitched battle filled with fierce Soma-on-Soma action has finally drawn to a close and we won!

achievements.title: Victory over Silver
achievements.description: You took Soma in hand and fought with all your might to try and make one who spoke of an "ideal" world see sense. And it seems you succeeded.

achievements.title: Victory over Chlorseraph
achievements.description: This ultimate mechanoid warrior was armed with an enormous green sword. Your defeat of him is proof that if you work together, you can overcome even the most insanely powerful opponents.

achievements.title: Victory over Xeromized Striegov
achievements.description: This unseemly character claimed to be a person of refinement, but proved that he would go to any lengths to satisfy his ugly appetites.

achievements.title: Victory over the Seraphim
achievements.description: Chlorseraph of the green blade, and Clinoseraph of the blue shield—seraphic siblings whose awe-inspiring twin attacks had to be seen to be believed.

achievements.title: Victory over Incarose Alt
achievements.description: Though she combined the arms and speed of Chlorseraph with the armor and power of Clinoseraph, she was ultimately alone, and unable to call on a power higher than her own.

achievements.title: Victory over Creed
achievements.description: He fought a bitter battle over two long millennia to save the one he loved and the world of Minera from whence he came. But when the moment of his end finally arrived, it was thanks to him that Kor was able to connect with the very first Spiria of all.

achievements.title: Victory over Faldealmeus
achievements.description: Though you suffered greatly at the hands of this gargantuan gatekeeper with his massive firepower and wide-ranging attacks, it only served to make the battle all the more of an exciting challenge, didn't it?

achievements.title: Manic Clearance
achievements.description: Congratulations! Not many people manage a clearance at the Manic difficulty level! The only thing left for you now is to take a plunge into the Unknown.

achievements.title: Unknown Clearance
achievements.description: Congratulations! You cleared the game at Unknown—the most hardcore difficulty level of all! There's not an enemy out there you can't take to pieces with ease!

achievements.title: Balloonatic
achievements.description: You've popped more balloons than there are stars in the sky! You're a stone-cold, certifiable balloonatic!

achievements.title: Arena Cleaner
achievements.description: Congratulations! You've sliced and diced your way through the arena, both alone and with a party by your side! This glorious achievement will surely stand unchallenged for millenia! Oh, uh. Don't look now, but that guy's staring at you kind of angrily.

achievements.title: Victory over Hubert and Pascal
achievements.description: This curious duo took to the field in their cute costumes and showed that they were more than just a pair of comedians.

achievements.title: Unbreakable Bond: Kor and Kohaku
achievements.description: This award stands as proof that you have forged an unbreakable bond between Kor and Kohaku, adding unassailable courage to the already formidable arsenal of spiritual weapons at our fair heroine's disposal.

achievements.title: Unbreakable Bond: Kor and Beryl
achievements.description: This award stands as proof that you have forged an unbreakable bond between Kor and Beryl. The sight of somebody single-mindedly chasing their dream is enough to spur anybody on. May her dreams of artistic greatness come true!

achievements.title: Unbreakable Bond: Kor and Chalcedony
achievements.description: This award stands as proof that you have forged an unbreakable bond between Kor and Chalcedony. Over the course of their many battles, both against one another and by each other's sides, they have learned an enormous amount. May the friendship between these brothers in arms last a thousand years!

achievements.title: Unbreakable Bond: Kohaku and Hisui
achievements.description: This award stands as proof that you have forged an unbreakable bond between the Hearts siblings. He may be a loudmouth, but it's all born of love, and why can't a big brother love his little sister more than anybody else?

achievements.title: Unbreakable Bond: Kohaku and Beryl
achievements.description: This award stands as proof that you have forged an unbreakable bond between Kohaku and Beryl. Want to see how powerful the ties of friendship can really be? Better hold on to your hats—this is going to be explosive!

achievements.title: Unbreakable Bond: Ines and Gall
achievements.description: This award stands as proof that you have forged an unbreakable bond between Ines and Gall. The power of parental love pumps through both these fierce fighters' veins like an unstoppable force!

achievements.title: Unbreakable Bond: Kunzite and Gall
achievements.description: This award stands as proof that you have forged an unbreakable bond between Kunzite and Gall. Just because he's a machine doesn't mean he can't have a Spiria, as anyone who has felt this mechanical warrior's warmth can attest.

title: This War of Mine: The Little Ones

achievements.title: Epilogue: This War of Mine: The Little Ones
achievements.description: What's next? What do we do? Where do we go?

achievements.title: Epilogue: War is over
achievements.description: The dogs of war have been raging around for so long. I survived and I hope I am not the only one.

achievements.title: Diary: Day 7
achievements.description: We’ve been holed up here for seven days, and we’ve managed to keep everyone alive - so far...

achievements.title: Diary: Vexing snow
achievements.description: Vexing snow. Half of the city’s buried so deep we can't get there. My kingdom for a snow plow...

achievements.title: Diary: Finished ransacking
achievements.description: We've explored every nook and cranny of our abode. Now we must venture outside for more supplies.

achievements.title: Note: Bless the radio
achievements.description: The radio is useful beyond expectations. We get weather reports, important news and music too.

achievements.title: Note: Distilled gold
achievements.description: We managed to distill some moonshine. Under siege, food and alcohol are always in high demand.

achievements.title: Note: Doubled the watch
achievements.description: It's crucial to secure our place against intruders. Two lookouts can watch out for each other.

achievements.title: Diary: Miraculous recovery
achievements.description: Either modern medicines work miracles, or perhaps some of us have really robust immune systems.

achievements.title: Diary: Patched up and ready to go
achievements.description: What good fortune. We managed to dress these grave wounds and now they are healing nicely.

achievements.title: Diary: Back from the brink
achievements.description: With just kind words and deeds, we helped one of us survive the darkest depression.

achievements.title: Diary: Hostel's open!
achievements.description: We now have enough beds for everyone except the one who has to go out and scavenge.

achievements.title: Diary: Shooting for five stars
achievements.description: For the first time since we wound up here all of us ate a hot meal. Let's not get used to it yet.

achievements.title: Diary: First blood
achievements.description: One of us had a brush with violent death. Let’s hope there’ll be no more such encounters.

achievements.title: Note: Creature comforts
achievements.description: Our place is starting to resemble a proper home and it keeps the spirits up.

achievements.title: Diary: Traces of lives
achievements.description: Every building we visit has a story to tell. What kind of story will we leave behind...?

achievements.title: Diary: We have wintered
achievements.description: The winter's gone. The freeze is over. We made it through... everyone made it! Amazing.

achievements.title: Epilogue: We made it!
achievements.description: At first we hardly dared to hope we’d make it, yet we're still here. It means something… right?

achievements.title: Diary: We've been everywhere
achievements.description: We've searched everywhere, and there’s almost nothing useful left. This war can't end soon enough.

achievements.title: Diary: We made a stand
achievements.description: Bandits came in packs like hungry wolves. We beat them back every night. And everyone survived.

achievements.title: Note: A bit of indulgence
achievements.description: We all indulged our addictions. It keeps the spirits up… and forget about health issues for once!

achievements.title: Note: The school of life
achievements.description: It’s crucial that kids learn to survive on their own. What if we don’t come back one night?

achievements.title: Diary: Our future
achievements.description: We made it! Schools will reopen soon. From now on, kids will live a normal life again.

achievements.title: Note: Avoid the worst
achievements.description: Attacking a place that shelters a kid… Atrocious! We stand together to protect our little one!

achievements.title: Note: Better days
achievements.description: Kids… they sometimes seem to be far away from this war. It’s heartwarming.

achievements.title: Diary: Bond for life
achievements.description: At least the kid has a new playmate. Maybe it will even be a break from our daily routine here.

achievements.title: Note: Everybody got to learn
achievements.description: Solidarity. That’s the first thing we have to teach to our children.

achievements.title: Diary: Our own playground
achievements.description: We wish we could be kids again and have fun with practically nothing.

achievements.title: Note: No more tears
achievements.description: Nothing is more beautiful to see than a child smile and play again.

achievements.title: The Never-Ending Path
achievements.description: "Sweet! You got all the trophies! You're really somethin'. Isn't that right, Ryu?" "You have done well to reach the end of this one journey. The path to becoming a true fighter still lies ahead, but let us take time to share the joy of your accomplishment."

achievements.title: Mastering The Basics
achievements.description: Why don't you try finishing up the tutorial? You might've mastered the first step, but nailing down the fundamentals is what's important.

achievements.title: Your Story Starts Here
achievements.description: Your first goal for Story Mode is just to clear it once. You can probably guess, but I cleared it with Master Zangief first!

achievements.title: Lucky We Met!
achievements.description: Whoa, I'm really mixing it with the celebrities here! C'mon, Rashid, you're the Raging Storm! Get out there and finish 5 Character Stories!

achievements.title: The 16 Trials
achievements.description: So you wish to learn Yoga? If that is truly the case, then first you must complete the Character Story with all characters. There is great merit in walking each of their individual paths.

achievements.title: One Step Forward
achievements.description: If you're at a loss for what to do, why not raise a character to level 5? It should help you realize what you're missing.

achievements.title: Quantity Over Quality
achievements.description: Level up 5 characters! Up to level 5 should do the trick. When it comes to food and fightin', it's quantity over quality, mate.

achievements.title: No Rest For The Wicked
achievements.description: Your stats are as pitiful as your strength, maggot! Come back when you've raised all characters to level 5.

achievements.title: Slow But Steady Wins The Race
achievements.description: Your objective should be to raise a single character to level 30. There is great meaning in accomplishing what is difficult. To find your answer, you must set your sights high.

achievements.title: Vindicated Honor
achievements.description: Raise your player level to 50. Level up that much and you'll be about ready to exact you revenge.

achievements.title: Burning Spirit
achievements.description: Your player level is a reflection of your passion! Aim for the stars, and reach level 100!

achievements.title: Number 2 Is The New Number 1
achievements.description: Niiihehe! 2, 20, 200! Such a glorious sound, I could say it twice more! 200! Raise you player level to 200! I already have, niiihehe!

achievements.title: Make A Name For Yourself
achievements.description: Why don't you see if you can collect 10 titles? There's nothin' like a good title! Even Mel said they make me look cool!

achievements.title: Sultan Of Titles
achievements.description: I am Rashid of the Turbulent Wind! You can change how you feel, just with a title! If you had 30 of them, you'd be set for the rest of your life!

achievements.title: Fighting On The Internet
achievements.description: Alright, time you fought 10 network battles! The Internet is like my backyard - not a place I tend to lose! (Excludes Battle Lounge)

achievements.title: All Going To Plan!
achievements.description: Master Zangief! I fought in 50 network battles! The ring came to life with the clash of burning spirits! (Excludes Battle Lounge)

achievements.title: A Fiendish Trap
achievements.description: Impossible! You fought in 300 network battles? Well then, the time for you to witness my Psycho Power draws near. Mwahaha! (Excludes Battle Lounge)

achievements.title: Waiting Is Half The Fun
achievements.description: Patience is key to any warrior's training. Fight in network battles 30 times using the standby function. The longer you wait, the greater the joy will be when you finally get picked.

achievements.title: I Know Kung Fu!
achievements.description: Congratulations on your first win! Keep practicing your Kung Fu in those Ranked Matches and I know you'll only get better and better!

achievements.title: Addicted To Winning
achievements.description: It seems you've won 10 Ranked Matches. Never forget how it feels to win, or your future will soon be eclipsed by defeat.

achievements.title: Working Up An Appetite!
achievements.description: 30 Ranked Matches already? Lemme go catch up to that! Dinner always tastes better after you've pummeled a bunch of chumps!

achievements.title: Ceaseless Effort
achievements.description: Ah, your 100th Ranked Match victory. That look in your eyes tells me it was a fulfilling battle. Go forward one step at a time, and never forget this feeling.

achievements.title: Bam, Bam, Win!
achievements.description: Winning 300 matches will put the word out for Matsuda Jiu-Jitsu! It'll be like, "the succesor or Matsuda Jiu-Jitsu, Laura Matsuda is right here!"

achievements.title: Always Someone Stronger
achievements.description: Why not try fighting someone stronger than you in a Ranked Match? There's a lot you can gain from fighting stronger opponents. Beat 10 of 'em and you'll understand.

achievements.title: Savoring The Win Streak
achievements.description: Achieved three consecutive victories in Ranked Matches, have you? It appears you are getting a handle on your power. Maintain your modesty, and focus on your training; the path ahead is long.

achievements.title: First Promotion!
achievements.description: Master Zangief sent me flowers to celebrate me moving up a league for the first time! I can't read the card with all these tears!

achievements.title: Muscles Bring Victory!
achievements.description: Did you make it to Silver League?! Horosho! You have very good muscle! You can get much stronger from now!

achievements.title: Let's fight someone strong!
achievements.description: Finally, Golden League! There are so many potential rivals! Now the fun really begins!

achievements.title: Go Out With A Bang
achievements.description: "Finishing with an EX Special Move sure feels good, old man!" "You finally understand then, young one? How about you try doing it 300 times?" "Wha?! You know how many years that'll take?!"

achievements.title: Critical Beauty
achievements.description: 300 Critical Art finishes... It would seem a crimson rose that blooms within an ugly heart can still be beautiful...

achievements.title: Not Over 'Til It's Over
achievements.description: When you get that feeling like "I can't let it end like this!", that's when you should use a V-Reversal. Practice it 100 times, and then you'll be able to pull it off in your sleep!

achievements.title: Enlightenment
achievements.description: There is a power that resides deep within you. If you wish to know what that power is, trigger a V-Skill 100 times. Do so, and that power will belong to you.

achievements.title: Sudden Reversal
achievements.description: You know, the V-Trigger is pretty handy for shifting the flow of battle. You'll know just how effective it is once you've triggered it 100 times.

achievements.title: Playing Favorites
achievements.description: You must set a character as your favorite! Can't decide who to choose? Niiihehehe! Well, you can't go wrong with Lord Bison!

achievements.title: All In A Name
achievements.description: You'll never stand out without an original title. Try choosing an appropriate title for me.

achievements.title: Failing To Prepare Is Preparing To Fail
achievements.description: Collect 30 replays, kid. Once you've done your prep and know your opponent's weaknesses, you'll be in control of the fight. Don't risk your life by rushing in blind.

achievements.title: See You In My Dreams!
achievements.description: Visualization is a crucial skill, so try watching 50 replays! I watched so many, I started seeing Master Zangief in my dreams!

achievements.title: Not-So-Secret Admirer
achievements.description: When someone sets their sights on you, don't you just wanna try even harder? Add someone to your Favorites and see what happens!

achievements.title: Global Network
achievements.description: I have the direct lines for all the world's leaders recorded in my pocketbook. You should have 30 names in your Favorites at the very least.

achievements.title: Bodybuilding Is Life
achievements.description: Go try out Training Mode for 30 minutes! "Bodybuilding never let man down." I borrowed that one from Master Zangief!

achievements.title: Win Or Die Tryin'
achievements.description: It's about time you cleared Survival Mode on normal difficulty. You know what happens if you refuse, don't you? Let's just say the only way you live is if you keep on winning!

achievements.title: A True Warrior's Spirit
achievements.description: A warrior's soul is ri...ripened in Survival Mode. Emerge victorious on hard difficulty and you'll be ready for me to co...consume.

achievements.title: Back From Hell
achievements.description: Feel like taking the plunge into Survival Mode on extreme? Come back alive, and I'll grant you an audience with none other than me, the great Lord Bison!

achievements.title: Priceless
achievements.description: You managed to get 1,000,000 FM. That's pretty good! The real value, however, is in the path you walked to earn that much.

achievements.title: The outfit is the highlight of battle
achievements.description: The true crème de la crème know how to give spectators a good show. Now go and gain new colors for your outfit.
